metadata.name: TradPunk-020
metadata.description:
CyberBaba II 

This is the year 2050. A country has advanced in the tech values. Also I am imagining that they will be able to balance out their culture and the advancements together. Forming a mixture of the present, past and the future. This is all about the art, How you imagine it, how you can tell your own story through this. This makes you feel more and think more....Baba ji got his own outfit!!


3d model from sketchfab
